id: pm-j5az
title: Add importers package scaffold and dependency-maintenance closeout
description: "Continue SDK/package platform maturity by adding a first-class pm package init --capability importers scaffold with runnable SDK tests, documenting the package-author flow, and folding current GitHub dependency/security findings into the same implementation lane. Duplicate check: searched all statuses for package init capability importers scaffold registerImporter registerExporter; related work pm-nhby, pm-pwai, pm-13bn, and pm-7qjk is closed and does not cover an importers scaffold."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[4]: agent-ux,"area:packages","area:sdk",github-deps
created_at: "2026-06-22T07:37:43.033Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-22T08:12:16.385Z"
author: codex-sdk-cli-continuation
parent: pm-ugqx
resolution: Implemented and verified a first-class importers scaffold plus dependency maintenance bundle.
expected_result: "Package authors can run pm package init --capability importers to get a runnable import/export starter with SDK tests, docs, completions, and dependency-maintenance updates remain green."
actual_result: "The importers scaffold generates command-safe import/export commands, declares importers plus schema for flag metadata, passes generated npm test and installed CLI temp smoke, updates docs/completions/tests, applies compatible Dependabot updates, and passes release gates with literal 100/100/100/100 coverage."
comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-22T07:43:42.762Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Investigation note: GitHub triage found open Dependabot PRs #334 checkout v7.0.0, #335 pnpm/action-setup v6.0.9, #336 softprops/action-gh-release v3.0.1, and #337 @types/node 26.0.0; no open GitHub issues and no open Dependabot security alerts. pnpm audit --audit-level moderate reported no known vulnerabilities. Duplicate check searched all statuses for importers package scaffolding; related pm-nhby, pm-pwai, pm-13bn, and pm-7qjk are closed and do not cover an importers scaffold."
  "2026-06-22T07:48:30.502Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Evidence: focused tests passed after scaffold fixes: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/extensions/extension-command.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/completion-command.spec.ts tests/integration/ci-workflow-contract.spec.ts (3 files, 206 tests). Manual temp smoke passed in /tmp/tmp.JZpoMLa3r6 with isolated PM_GLOBAL_PATH: pm init demo --force, pm package init ./starter-importers --capability importers, npm install --no-save local checkout, npm test, pm install ./starter-importers --project, pm starter importers items import --source tickets --json, and pm starter importers items export --destination archive --json. Install activation diagnostics reported failed_count 0 and command discovery exposed starter importers items import/export/ping."
  "2026-06-22T07:59:36.520Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Evidence: repo-wide gates passed. node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage reported 242 files / 4834 tests and literal 100/100/100/100 coverage (Statements 30546/30546, Branches 23823/23823, Functions 5107/5107, Lines 29341/29341). pnpm quality:docs-skills passed. pnpm quality:static passed. pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift returned ok with pre-existing validate_resolution_missing_fields:227 warning and history_drift ok. pnpm changelog:pm:check passed with pm-changelog 2026.6.20 and CHANGELOG.md unchanged. pnpm contracts:check passed. pnpm audit --audit-level moderate reported no known vulnerabilities. pnpm security:scan found no credential-like secrets. sentry-telemetry-gate best-effort passed: Sentry 0 critical/high blockers over 14 days, telemetry finish_error_rate_pct 1.23, failures_without_error_code_rows 0. pnpm release:gates passed, including npx packed package smoke and package-first dogfood."
  "2026-06-22T08:00:07.838Z",codex-sdk-cli-continuation,"Dependency note: after applying @types/node 26.0.0, pnpm outdated --format json only reports commander 15.0.0. npm metadata for commander@15.0.0 requires node >=22.12.0, so it is intentionally deferred because pm-cli still supports node >=20 and CI validates Node 20."
  "2026-06-22T08:12:16.385Z",codex,"Review follow-up: applied Gemini feedback on PR #338 by generating importer/exporter action ids with the same space-separated command path shown to users instead of hyphenated internal ids. Re-ran focused tests and build after the patch: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/extensions/extension-command.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/completion-command.spec.ts tests/integration/ci-workflow-contract.spec.ts passed 206 tests; pnpm build passed. Manual temp smoke after the review fix passed in isolated temp directories: pm init demo --force, package init ./starter-importers --capability importers, npm install --no-save checkout, npm test, project install, starter importers items import --source tickets, and starter importers items export --destination archive all succeeded with expected importer/exporter results."
